.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Onestopenglish&amp;rft.atitle=What+is+CLIL%3F&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.onestopenglish.com%2Fclil%2Fwhat-is-clil%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AContent+and+language+integrated+learning\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=COM:2003:0449:FIN:EN:PDF\">Commission Of The European Communities Promoting Language Learning and Linguistic Diversity: An Action Plan 2004 \u2013 2006</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=OJ:C:2008:320:0001:0003:EN:PDF\">Journal of the European Union Council Resolution of 21 November 2008 on a European strategy for multilingualism</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">An educational project called <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://e-clil.uws.ac.uk/\">ECLIL</a> was also supported from the European Union within the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://eacea.ec.europa.eu/llp/index_en.php\">Lifelong Learning Programme EACEA Agency</a>, to develop interactive resources for European schools.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Coyle, D., Hood, P. &amp; Marsh, D. (2010). CLIL. Cambridge: C.U.P.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Lorenzo, F., Trujillo, F. &amp; Vez, M. (2011). Educaci\u00f3n biling\u00fce. Integraci\u00f3n de contenidos y segundas lenguas. Madrid: S\u00edntesis.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Cenoz-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Cenoz_9-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Cenoz_9-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Cenoz, Gennessee &amp; Gorter (2014). \"Critical analysis of CLIL: Taking stock and looking forward\". <i>Applied Linguistics</i>. <b>35</b> (3): 243\u2013262.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Applied+Linguistics&amp;rft.atitle=Critical+analysis+of+CLIL%3A+Taking+stock+and+looking+forward.&amp;rft.volume=35&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=243-262&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft.au=Cenoz%2C+Gennessee+%26+Gorter&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AContent+and+language+integrated+learning\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Dalton-Puffer-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Dalton-Puffer_10-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Dalton-Puffer_10-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Dalton-Puffer_10-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Dalton-Puffer, Llinares, Lorenzo &amp; Nikula (2014). \"<span style=\"padding-left:0.2em;\">\"</span>You can stand under my umbrella\": Immersion, clil and bilingual education. A response to Cenoz, Genesee &amp; Gorter (2013)\". <i>Applied Linguistics</i>. <b>35</b> (2): 213\u2013218.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Applied+Linguistics&amp;rft.atitle